org.apache.cordova

Interface CordovaWebViewEngine.Client

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CordovaWebViewImpl.EngineClient
    Enclosing interface:
    CordovaWebViewEngine

    public static interface CordovaWebViewEngine.Client
    Contains methods that an engine uses to communicate with the parent CordovaWebView. Methods may be added in future cordova versions, but never removed.
